ygData.messageBody:
Hail Fellow EQ Sister!

I play Rain D'Terrah on Tarew Marr - Level 26 Warrior. I look forward to
hearing and corresponding with all of EQ Women for some fun talk and shared
resources.

Rain

-----Original Message-----
From: MJ Solomon <mjsol@...>
To: EQ_women@onelist.com <EQ_women@onelist.com>
Date: Wednesday, June 16, 1999 8:29 AM
Subject: Re: [EQ_women] Welcome to EQ_women@onelist.com


>From: "MJ Solomon" <mjsol@...>
>
>Hod do I respond?
>Do I have to go to onelist site, or does this message go to the list??
>-----Original Message-----
>From: EQ_women-owner@onelist.com <EQ_women-owner@onelist.com>
>To: mjsol@... <mjsol@...>
>Date: Tuesday, June 15, 1999 11:03 PM
>Subject: [EQ_women] Welcome to EQ_women@onelist.com
>
>
>>Hi there, and welcome to EQ Women! This mailing list is
>>for women who play the game Everquest to meet eachother
>>and chat.
>>
>>Please feel free to post an intro message with your
>>character's name, race, class, level and server
>>(and anything else you'd like).
>>For example:
>>
>> "Hi everyone! I play Iuna, a 17th level wood elf druid
>> on Mithaniel Marr. I'm looking forward to
>> chatting on the list."
>>
>>If you ever want to unsubscribe, go to the ONElist web site, at
>>www.onelist.com, and select the User Center link from the menu bar
>>on the left. This menu will also let you change your subscription
>>between digest and normal mode. This list is for
>> women only, so please respect this policy and unsubscribe if you
>>are not a woman!.
>>
>>Have fun,
>>
>>Christina
>>
>
>
